high_descs: Turn around, step forward, then turn right to face a nightstand.
Pick up the CD to the left of the lamp.
Turn right, step forward, turn right, step forward, then turn around to face a nightstand.
Open the drawer of the nightstand, place the CD to the left side, close the drawer.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to walk towards the sofa.
Pick up the CD on the right side of the sofa.
Turn right and return to the nightstand.
Open the draw and place the CD to the right of the other CD in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Find two CDs within the room and place them in a nightstand drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the black table.
Pick up the CD on the table.
Make a 360 degree turn and look at the table again.
Open the drawer on the table and put the CD inside. Close the door.
Turn left and walk to face the chair.
Pick up the CD on the chair.
Turn right the left and go back to the table.
Open the drawer, put the CD inside, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two CD's in the drawer of the black table.

high_descs: Turn around, then face the black table to your right.
Take the CD from the black table in front of you.
Turn around in a circle, face the black table in front of you.
Open the black table drawer in front of you, place the CD inside the black table and close the cabinet.
Turn left and face the grey couch on your right.
Take the CD off the grey couch in front of you.
Turn right, then left and head towards the black table in front of you.
Open the black table drawer in front of you, place the CD inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put CD's away in black table.
